**Never:** `rec`, destructuring with `with`. **Always:** Explicit destructuring, `nixfmt`, namespaced options, `let-in` over `rec`, platform guards for Linux/Darwin deps, `config.home.homeDirectory` (no hardcoded `/home/`), multi-system support, `lib.mkIf`/`mkMerge` for conditions, `assert` for validation.

**Validation:** `nix flake check` | `nixfmt .` | `nix eval .#packages.x86_64-linux.default` | `nix flake show`

**Option types:** `lib.types.bool|str|int|package|listOf|attrsOf|path|nullOr|enum|submodule` — use nixos-mcp to look up.
